{"content": "I need to multiply 282 \u00d7 371 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 282\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 162 + 72 + 2 = 236\u2081\u2080\n- 371\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 1\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 1\u00d71 = 243 + 63 + 1 = 307\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 236 \u00d7 307 = 72,452\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 72452 \u00f7 9 = 8050 r 2\n- 8050 \u00f7 9 = 894 r 4\n- 894 \u00f7 9 = 99 r 3\n- 99 \u00f7 9 = 11 r 0\n- 11 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 2\n- 1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: **120342\u2089**\n\n120342", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 342}